                        <head>Volume V: Byzantine Inscriptions</head>
                        <p>This is the first electronic edition of the Byzantine Inscriptions from the Northern Black Sea
                        (IOSPE vol. V). The introduction, editions and commentary are by Andrey Vinogradov,
                        English translations are by Irene Polinskaya. The inscriptions were encoded following
                        the <ref target="http://epidoc.sf.net/">EpiDoc</ref> Guidelines for use of XML for ancient
                        documentry editions, and the website and supporting materials are the work of Gabriel Bodard,
                        Irene Polinskaya and colleagues at the Department of Digital Humanities, King's College London.</p>
                        <div><head>Contents</head>
                        <list type="simple">
